{
  "chapter": 64,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十四回\"祸水\"主要讲述三条线索的交织。龙啸云得知即将成为金钱帮第二把手，与龙小云商议上官金虹是否会反悔，志得意满。上官金虹在处理帮务时收到林仙儿的密信，与荆无命一同前往松林。松林中，林仙儿以美色迷惑吕凤先，引其与上官金虹对峙。上官金虹仅凭气势便不战而屈人之兵，吕凤先未出手即崩溃。林仙儿见风使舵投向上官金虹，二人谈论李寻欢时，阿飞突然出现欲杀上官金虹。林仙儿阻止阿飞，称上官金虹是她的\"恩人\"，阿飞陷入两难。本章深刻展现了林仙儿的狡诈与上官金虹的霸气，同时阿飞对林仙儿的痴情使其沦为被操控的棋子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "她为什么不肯跟我一起来？为什么不肯分享我的光彩？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你想这次上官金虹会不会亲自来迎接我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "当然会，而且仪式一定很隆重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我也这么想，我既是他的兄弟，他给我面子，岂非也正如给自己面子？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "他来接我时，你想我是该称他帮主，还是该唤他大哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "当然该称大哥，孩儿今后也要改口，唤他一声伯父了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "有这样的伯父，真是你的运气，只怕……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "李寻欢既然未死，他会不会食言反悔？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "天下英雄都已知道此事，帖子也早就发了出去，他再反悔，岂非自食其言，以后说的话还有谁相信？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "不错，武林中人之所以信服他，就因为他令出如山，言出法随，现在他就算想反悔，也来不及了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "李寻欢呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你不后悔么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "后悔？我为什么要后悔？有了你，任何男人都不会觉得后悔。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我真的那么好？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你当然好，比我想像中还好，比任何人想像中都要好……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "现在不行……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你……你还要留着力气对付上官金虹。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我对付了你，还可以再对付他。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你千万莫要看轻了他，他绝不如你想像中那么好对付。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你认为我不如他强？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我不是这意思，只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你只要杀了上官金虹，天下就都是我们的了，以后我们的日子还长着哩，你现在何必着急。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "想不到你真的这么关心，我——",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "吕凤先？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "很好，吕凤先总算还值得我出手。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你若非上官金虹，我也不屑杀你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "她绝不会过去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你已败了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我不杀你，因为你已不值得我出手！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我劝你不如还是死了的好。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "现在我才真的服了你了！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "荆无命杀人出手虽然快，但你却比他更快十倍！因为……因为你杀人根本用不着出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "那只因到现在我还未遇着一个人配我出手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这世上能令你出手的人确实不多……也许只有一个。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "李寻欢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这人好像随时都可能倒下去，又好像永远不会倒下去，有时候我实在想不透他是个怎么样的人，君子？呆子？还是英雄？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你对他好像一直都很有兴趣。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我一定要对他有兴趣，因为我不愿死在他手上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "一个人对自己的情人就算再有兴趣，日子久了，也会渐渐变淡的，但对自己的敌人，反而不同了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "兴趣也有很多种，你是恨他，怕他，还是爱他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你现在好像也渐渐变得会吃醋了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "阿飞呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他当然也会吃醋。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我只是在问你，你为何不杀他？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我也想问你，荆无命为何不杀他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我本要你自己下手的，你难道不忍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "要杀人很容易，若要一个人甘心听你的话，那就困难多了，到现在为止，我还没有找到一个像他那么样听话的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我来找你，并不是为了要跟你吵架，你若真的要我杀他，以后的机会还多的是，我一定听你的话。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我从来不在背后杀人，但这一次，却也是例外！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你还不回头？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "在背后杀人，也一样能杀得死的，又何必回头？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "阿飞！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你果然来了，我知道你一定会来的……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我知道你回去见不到我，一定会很着急，一定会找我。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "为了找我，你一定吃了不少苦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我已找到你，这已足够。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你就想用这柄剑来杀我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这柄剑又如何？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这柄剑不能杀人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "无论什么样的剑，都可以杀人的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "但这却不是你用的剑，你若用这柄剑，只能杀得死你自己。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若不信，不妨试试。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你要杀他？你可知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他是我的恩人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    }
